<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Köln</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Peter I. Volckamer, Ratsherr zu Nürnberg, an und bittet um gütliche Anhörung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_492" id="245v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_492_r1l1">Cölen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_492_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Wir <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l3"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeÿr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l4">dem vvir <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etwas <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan></del> notdurft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l5">mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit cʒe <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / VVas derſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Ratgeſell von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> mit ew red vnd an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l7">ewr vveiſheit bring / daʒ Jr Jm des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l8">ew <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> gütlıch vnd <expan>fruntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvillen tün vvöllet / Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l10">frewntſchaft ſünderlıch vvol getrawen / vnd in <expan>ſölıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l11">vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> vmb ewr erberkeit cʒü allen <expan>cʒeıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l12">mit vvıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> vvöllen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_492_r1l13">in Craſtino <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> Margarethe <expan>virg<ex>inis</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_492" id="245v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Cölen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir
                                <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> czü <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ersamkeit <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeyr,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesellen, dem wir
                                <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> etwas <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> notdurft
                        mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit cze
                        <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, was
                        derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> ratgesell von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> mit ew red und an ewr weisheit bring, daz ir
                        im des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ew
                            <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> gütlich und
                            <expan>fruntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tün wöllet, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan> frewntschaft sünderlich wol getrawen und in
                                <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> umb ewr erberkeit czü allen
                                <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit willen
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> wöllen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                        crastino <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> Margarethe
                                <expan>virg<ex>inis.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
